    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable way to get from A to B without breaking the bank? This vehicle is in fair condition and ready for its next adventure! It shows some honest wear from its time on the road, but it remains a functional and steady performer for anyone seeking a practical daily driver. This is a great opportunity to own a dependable ride at a very accessible price!",
